- **Time Complexity**: Average and Worst case - O(n^2), Best case - O(n) when nearly sorted.
- **Space Complexity**: O(1), in-place.
```cpp
void insertionSort(int arr[], int n) {
    int key, j;
    for (int i = 1; i < n; i++) {
        key = arr[i];
        j = i - 1;
        while (j >= 0 && arr[j] > key) {
            arr[j + 1] = arr[j];
            j = j - 1;
        }
        arr[j + 1] = key;
    }
}
```

### Selection Sort
- **Time Complexity**: Always O(n^2).
- **Space Complexity**: O(1), in-place.
